SpeedCard - An exceedingly simple flashcard sequencer, for memorization.
Linux Version: Written in python, using GTK+ and Glade for an GUI.
Tested on Ubuntu.
Mac and Windows are planned, but haven't been written.
Currently, a demonstration .csv file of spanish vocabulary words is provided.
Enjoy!

Usage:
To run, doubleclick on the SpeedCard executing file and click Run in the following prompt.
To change the wordlist, rename the wordlist.csv file, and make another with the format
The word you want define, seperated by a comma, then the definition.
(Commandline usage: SpeedCard (wordlistfile))
